*plruby-0.5.4-r1 (20 Oct 2012)

  20 Oct 2012; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +plruby-0.5.4-r1.ebuild:
  Add missing dependency on postgresql-base. Convert to EAPI=4 to fix
  deprecations. Fixes bug 438926.

  26 Dec 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -plruby-0.4.2.ebuild,
  -plruby-0.5.3.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

  04 Dec 2011; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> plruby-0.5.4.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #391325

  28 Nov 2011; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> plruby-0.5.4.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #391325

*plruby-0.5.4 (27 Jun 2010)

  27 Jun 2010; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +plruby-0.5.4.ebuild,
  +files/plruby-0.5.4-fix-build-system.patch:
  Version bump. Convert to ruby-ng. Fix build system to work with other ruby
  versions installed.

  17 Jun 2010; Patrick Lauer <patrick@gentoo.org> plruby-0.4.2.ebuild,
  plruby-0.5.3.ebuild:
  Migrating away from deprecated postgres virtuals

  21 May 2008; Tiziano Müller <dev-zero@gentoo.org> plruby-0.4.2.ebuild,
  plruby-0.5.3.ebuild:
  Changed dependency for postgresql from dev-db/postgresql to
  virtual/postgresql-server

  18 Apr 2008; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> plruby-0.5.3.ebuild:
  stable on amd64

  14 Mar 2008; Caleb Tennis <caleb@gentoo.org> -plruby-0.4.9.ebuild,
  -plruby-0.5.1.ebuild:
  remove old versions

